						p The is no substitute for good content. 
						p Except perhaps an amazing user experience. 
						p Technology should support the experience. Not the other way around.
						p The value of a quality web and mobile presence continues to increase every day. 
						p It is difficult to overestimate the value of good design. 
						p Intuition is great, but data is better. 
